DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
     mmoopphheerrdd reads a list of rules and acts on each incoming mail delivery
     attempt based on various criteria and existing states.

     Available options are:

     --hh      Show usage message.

     --ff      Run in foreground, don't detach from the controlling terminal.

     --CC      Check configuration file syntax and exit.

     --dd _l_e_v_e_l
             Set logging severity level to _l_e_v_e_l.

     --cc _f_i_l_e
             Read configuration from _f_i_l_e.

     --pp _p_i_d_f_i_l_e
             Create a PID file in _p_i_d_f_i_l_e.

FFIILLEESS
     @sysconfdir@/mopher/mopherd.conf
             Configuration file for the mopher daemon.

     @sysconfdir@/mopher/mopherd.acl
             List of rules enforced by the mopher daemon.

